❗️A joint meeting of the Environmental Policy and Agrarian and Land Policy Committees was held to discuss the provisions of the draft law on plant protection products and fertilizers (No. 11062). plants provided for by the provisions of this draft law;
- the interrelationship of the provisions of the draft law with the provisions of the Law of Ukraine "On ensuring chemical safety and management of chemical products" No. 2804-IX;
- comprehensive review of draft laws No. 11062 and 8340; - insurance of economic activity in the field of storage and use of plant protection products;
- carrying out state tests of plant protection products, evaluation of active substances of plant protection products, antidotes and synergists;
- the need for a transition period in case of adoption of the relevant Law.

Based on the results of the meeting, a decision was made to create a Working Group to develop the draft law. 📲 Details

